column1:
1. Setup from AWS console CloudFront Dashboard or by clicking on Create Distribution button.
  2. Enter the id of distribution in Distribution Id field and save the configuration.
  3. Click Check Status button to get the Domain Name (URL) and status of the Distribution.
  4. Distribution only works when it's status is Deployed.
  5. Use CloudFront Distribution Domain Name (URL) in Base URL for User Media Files instead of S3 bucket URL.
